# Security Keywords List -- EXAMPLE TEMPLATE
# This file shows the format for security-keywords.txt
# DO NOT put real keywords in this file -- it is committed to the repo.
#
# Usage:
#   1. Copy this file to security-keywords.txt
#   2. Replace the examples below with your actual sensitive terms
#   3. Run: scripts/encrypt-keywords.sh
#   4. Commit the resulting security-keywords.enc (NOT the .txt)
#
# Format:
#   - One keyword/phrase per line
#   - Lines starting with # are comments (ignored)
#   - Matching is case-insensitive
#   - Empty lines are ignored

# Client names
acme-corp
globex-industries

# Project codenames
project-phoenix
operation-sunrise

# Internal identifiers
internal-api-v2
staging-db-cluster

# Domain-specific terms
secret-endpoint-name
